你能帮我想想办法吗？我小妹耶
Listen, can you help me out for a second? She's my little sister.

51
00:05:15,273 --> 00:05:16,608
她叫艾波儿，我是茱恩
She's April, I'm June,

52
00:05:16,733 --> 00:05:18,693
她等着我明天陪她走红毯
she's counting on me to march her down the aisle tomorrow.

53
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:20,070
好温馨
That's very sweet,

54
00:05:20,237 --> 00:05:22,864
搭11点50分的晚班机 您明早就会抵达
but the 11:50 will get you there tomorrow morning with plenty of time.

55
00:05:23,365 --> 00:05:24,908
登机证，先生？
Your boarding pass, sir?

56
00:05:27,118 --> 00:05:29,454
有时事出必有因
Sometimes things happen for a reason.

57
00:05:31,289 --> 00:05:32,415
一路顺风，米勒先生
Enjoy your flight, Mr. Miller.

58
00:05:32,582 --> 00:05:33,750
谢谢
Thank you.

59
