别动，米勒
Don't move, Miller.

178
00:13:34,313 --> 00:13:36,983
好，你打算怎么做？ 你打算怎么做？
So what are you gonna do? What are you gonna do?

179
00:13:37,066 --> 00:13:39,861
你打算让这机会溜掉？
You're just gonna let this opportunity pass you by?

180
00:13:39,944 --> 00:13:40,945
不，当然不行
No, of course you're not.

181
00:13:41,029 --> 00:13:43,322
你要走出去，主动一点
You're gonna walk right through that door, you're gonna get it right.

182
00:13:43,406 --> 00:13:44,741
反正你也不是第一次主动
